{"pv23:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv23:0.2":"Ubbarivagga ","pv23:0.3":"11. Suttapetavatthu ","pv23:1.1":"“Aham pure pabbajitassa bhikkhuno, ","pv23:1.2":"Suttam adasim upasankamma yacita; ","pv23:1.3":"Tassa vipako vipulaphalupalabbhati, ","pv23:1.4":"Bahuka ca me uppajjare vatthakotiyo. ","pv23:2.1":"Pupphabhikinnam ramitam vimanam, ","pv23:2.2":"Anekacittam naranarisevitam; ","pv23:2.3":"Saham bhunjami ca parupami ca, ","pv23:2.4":"Pahutavitta na ca tava khiyati. ","pv23:3.1":"Tasseva kammassa vipakamanvaya, ","pv23:3.2":"Sukhanca satanca idhupalabbhati; ","pv23:3.3":"Saham gantva punadeva manusam, ","pv23:3.4":"Kahami punnani nayayyaputta man”ti. ","pv23:4.1":"“Satta tuvam vassasata idhagata, ","pv23:4.2":"Jinna ca vuddha ca tahim bhavissasi; ","pv23:4.3":"Sabbeva te kalakata ca nataka, ","pv23:4.4":"Kim tattha gantvana ito karissasi”ti. ","pv23:5.1":"“Satteva vassani idhagataya me, ","pv23:5.2":"Dibbanca sukhanca samappitaya; ","pv23:5.3":"Saham gantvana punadeva manusam, ","pv23:5.4":"Kahami punnani nayayyaputta man”ti. ","pv23:6.1":"So tam gahetvana pasayha bahayam, ","pv23:6.2":"Paccanayitvana therim sudubbalam; ","pv23:6.3":"“Vajjesi annampi janam idhagatam, ","pv23:6.4":"‘Karotha punnani sukhupalabbhati’. ","pv23:7.1":"Dittha maya akatena sadhuna, ","pv23:7.2":"Peta vihannanti tatheva manussa; ","pv23:7.3":"Kammanca katva sukhavedaniyam, ","pv23:7.4":"Deva manussa ca sukhe thita paja”ti. ","pv23:8.1":"Suttapetavatthu ekadasamam. "}